Synergy::

"Oh, brother, and I thought the geezer was bad.  Very well, this 
way."  Synergy transforms to her tank mode and drives toward the 
Tripred base.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Rudra656@a... wrote:
> ::Kaiser/The Dragoon::
>        Kaiser shrugs and turns away from both of them sulking 
slightly.  He 
> mumbles quietly to himself.  "I thought my way was better, bah."
> 
>        The unknown bot turns to face the seemingly sane Synergy.  
His 
> expression is unreadable and the air around his body seems to 
shimmer 
> slightly.  When he speaks there are two voices speaking almost as 
an echo.  
> "We are The Dragoon.  We live to serve, but we have no master.  
Guide us to 
> your commander."
